QUALIFIER.NAME: Description
QUALIFIER.VALUE: CIM_ElementView is used to associate an instance of CIM_View with an instance representing one or more instances of managed resources that contribute to the view.

QUALIFIER.NAME: Description
QUALIFIER.VALUE: Antecedent shall be a reference to a CIM_ManagedElement that is an instance in the normalized representation of the managed resource that contributes to the view.

QUALIFIER.NAME: Description
QUALIFIER.VALUE: Dependent shall be a reference to an instance of CIM_View that represents a de-normalized or aggregate view of one or more instances that contribute to the view.
